title: Independent candidate Usama Asghar Ali wins PP-282 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Usama Asghar Ali Gujjar has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-282, Layyah-IV by securing 53,887 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Istehkam-e-Pakistan Party candidate, Syed Rafaqat Ali Gilani who bagged 23,897 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 59.02%.
